## R-SegBar Segmented Token Progress Bar — Implementation Review

### Criterion Assessment

| Spec Item | Status | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Relay-D15 Composable interface | ✅ pass | `ProfessionSegment`, `TooltipBarEntry` types match spec. |
| Relay-D15 Component props | ✅ pass | `segments`, `totalBudget`, `totalUsed`, `tooltipEntries`, `warnThreshold`, `dangerThreshold` — correct types and defaults (0.7/0.9). |
| Relay-D15 Segment rendering | ✅ pass | Width proportional to `totalBudget`, min-width 2px, color from palette. |
| Relay-D15 Budget warning classes | ✅ pass | `budget-warn` at 70%, `budget-danger` at 90%. |
| Relay-D15 Tooltip inline (per P4.2) | ✅ pass | No separate `AgentBreakdownTooltip.vue` — tooltip inlined per plan decision. |
| Relay-D15 Hover delays | ✅ pass | 80ms show delay, 150ms hide debounce. |
| Relay-D15 Accessibility | ✅ pass | `role="progressbar"`, `aria-valuenow`, `aria-valuemax`, `aria-label`. |
| Relay-D15 Animations | ✅ pass | Segment width 300ms ease-out, tooltip fade-in 150ms ease, fade-out 100ms ease. |
| Relay-D15 RelayView integration | ✅ pass | Old budget bar removed, `SegmentedProgressBar` in place. |
| Relay-D15 CSS cleanup | ✅ pass | Old budget-bar and cost-panel CSS removed. |

